    bullet_points:
      - Designed and implemented a highly available, distributed key-value store in Go utilizing the Raft consensus algorithm.
      - Achieved sub-10ms read/write latencies at 50,000 requests per second by optimizing network serialization with gRPC.
      - Integrated Prometheus and Grafana for real-time monitoring of consensus latency and system health.

