    links:
      GitHub: https://github.com/janedoe/autopredict
    tags: [ai, research]
    bullet_points:
      - Engineered a convolutional neural network pipeline in PyTorch to classify medical scan abnormalities with 94.2% accuracy.
      - Reduced model training time by 35% through custom data augmentation strategies and multi-GPU parallelization.
      - Authored a research paper detailing findings, accepted for presentation at a regional machine learning symposium.

  - title: EventSync - Real-Time Collaborative Editor
    date: Sep 2024 - Dec 2024
    tech_stack: [TypeScript, React, Node.js, Socket.io, Redis, MongoDB]
    links:
      GitHub: https://github.com/janedoe/eventsync
    tags: [sde]
