      - Built a collaborative rich-text editor using Operational Transformation (OT) algorithms to handle concurrent edits.
      - Handled up to 1,000 concurrent active users per room by implementing a Redis Pub/Sub backend for message synchronization.
      - Designed an intuitive React interface with typing indicators and cursor tracking.

